@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ooixfk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((tmp - (tmp + 0.95 / v0 + 0.91)) * 0.06)
    tmp = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.87 / v2 + 0.86)) * wp.exp((v0 + 0.13 + v2 + 0.53)))
    v0 = ((v1 * wp.sin(v2 + 0.06)) * v1)
    data[tid] = v0
